At first I didn't know what to expect, but I really am loving this game/simulation! It worths all of its cents.

ATTENTION KEYBOARD USERS-The game is still fun with a keyboard, I don't have virtual reality and that hasn't in anyway or form reduced my experience or fun.

PROS:
It is really relaxing;
The environment is beautiful and makes this a great experience;
You can see the other souls" (players) floating around in a daize to find their own path.
Many uplifting quotes!
The sounds in game are very VERY realistic.
It is very colourful and bright;
You can collect apples and shells :3;
It has a gigantic statue of Buddha;
It has fishes and turtles swimming in the ocean <3;
The place is very relaxing and trully makes you dive into the experience;
CONS:
Be aware that this game was released recently!
Sometimes you get disconnected from the server (instantly connected again but spawn at the start);
When you dive into the water it looks like you're sinking.
Sidenotes: You have no objectives to complete in this game
